data.message: This song is not good at all lol (Ems my fav rapper of all time, I dont have to like every song). Its just Em talking over piano keys and its so out of place compared to all his old music. This sounds like it should be the final song on the album not the first single. Hoping every other song on the album is more like the Slim Shady lp, Marshall Mathers lp and The Eminem Show...
